"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-paralympics-tickets-popular-with-parisians-who-snubbed-the-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  FILE PHOTO: Paris 2024 Paralympics - Paris, France - August 18, 2024  Workers work to convert the Eiffel Tower Stadium from the beach volleyball venue to the Paralympic blind football venue for the coming Paris 2024 Paralympic Games REUTERS/Abdul Saboor/File Photo    PublishedAug 23, 2024, 04:18 PM  UpdatedAug 24, 2024, 04:33 PM  PARIS - Parisians are the main buyers of tickets for the Paralympic Games, the organisers said, rushing to grab a second opportunity to see competitions in some of the Games' spectacular venues, after many chose to snub the Olympics or missed out on tickets.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.9999999999240572, \"rank\": 7.584238829677421e-11, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703097123, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.777835236537345e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In July, Parisians had left the city in droves ahead of the Olympics, with entire neighbourhoods turned eerily quiet as residents decamped as they feared the disturbance and traffic problems many thought the Games would bring.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Games turned out to be a global success.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics will allow them to see Olympic sports in the same venues, including below the Eiffel Tower or in the gardens of the Versailles palace outside Paris.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.777835236537345e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisers said that of the more than 1.75 million tickets already sold ahead of the Aug 28 start of the Paralympics, 92 per cent came from French buyers, with buyers from the Ile-de-France region around Paris taking the lion's share of 73 per cent.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5061354380672239, \"rank\": 0.5015492374558704, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele-de-France\", \"score\": 0.999999999979309, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ile-de-France region\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele-de-France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele-de-France\"}, {\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.777835236537345e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisian Mathieu Bucella is set to boost these numbers a little further.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am seriously thinking about it because I am a bit annoyed that I did not think of getting tickets for the (Olympic) Games, so this is my second chance,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers said several sessions were nearly sold out already, notably wheelchair fencing and para taekwondo in Grand Palais, para track cycling in Saint Quentin, para equestrian in Chateau de Versailles and blind football at Champ de Mars.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Quentin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2296159185274276e-14, \"text\": \"Saint Quentin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Quentin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Quentin\"}, {\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chateau de Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were watching the Olympic Games on TV, but after that you get that gut feeling that you want to come and see everything with your own eyes,\\\" Mexican tourist Arlet Haro said.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2156, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9981895172242276, \"rank\": 0.0017410348848186194, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US tourist Asad Rahman said he was glad to have come to Paris for the Paralympics.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2190, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8961706378976929, \"rank\": 0.11585651319383651, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Asad\", \"score\": 0.9999929488161192, \"rank\": 7.0459904316115795e-06, \"text\": \"Asad\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Asad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Asad\"}, {\"begin\": 2206, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._R._Rahman\", \"score\": 0.9999999838755685, \"rank\": 1.612341931007762e-08, \"text\": \"Rahman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._R._Rahman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._R._Rahman\"}, {\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.777835236537345e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Things are a little bit more open than what we heard with the Olympics, where they closed off some areas.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it works out, as a tourist,\\\" he said next to the Eiffel Tower, where workers were converting the beach volleyball pitch into a blind football pitch.\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": []}, {\"se